br />\n為何做英華校長不容易？Rick堅定地說：「因為我哋學生有反抗意志，有自由意志！」//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31180/%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-%E9%84%AD%E9%88%9E%E5%82%91-%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-31192/%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E4%BB%94%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%84%AD%E9%88%9E%E5%82%91%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%96%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E5%94%94%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E3%80%81%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%80%E8%A8%80%E5%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F31180%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%2588%259E%25E5%2582%2591-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7-31192%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%2588%259E%25E5%2582%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BB%2596%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25BE%259E%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E3%2580%2581%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25BF%2582%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%25A0%2582&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=59dc2f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31180/%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-%E9%84%AD%E9%88%9E%E5%82%91-%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7-31192/%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E4%BB%94%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%84%AD%E9%88%9E%E5%82%91%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%96%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%A2%E6%9C%9B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%9E%E4%BE%86%E5%94%94%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E3%80%81%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%80%E8%A8%80%E5%A0%82</a>"},{"pid":"9781172f035cf8906322600d77058a3c314cca01","tid":2071574,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"校長都要走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma